|    07. CONTENT           |    1 LLM call / video
|                          |    2 prompt variants:
|  INFIELD/COMPILATION:    |
|   Per approach:          |    31 techniques taxonomy
|    - Techniques used     |    22 topics taxonomy
|    - Topics discussed    |
|    - Turn-by-turn phases |    open -> pre_hook ->
|    - Hook/investment     |    post_hook -> close
